  "detailed_description": "Have you ever dreamed about building a terrarium? Do you already have one, but it’s not enough? Or maybe you want to test yourself before making the real one? Terrarium Builder is a game for you! In Terrarium Builder you can design and create realistic terrariums with the following features:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Terrain Sculpting</h2>Sculpt the terrain with different brushes, so that you can achieve the shape that you want.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/0874fce21c666776b3908bd26d3e4eb4.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/0874fce21c666776b3908bd26d3e4eb4.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/0874fce21c666776b3908bd26d3e4eb4.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Terrain Painting</h2>Paint typical surfaces like grass, moss, and the terrain itself.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d9490acc228ce31f4e851da84bdda45c.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d9490acc228ce31f4e851da84bdda45c.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d9490acc228ce31f4e851da84bdda45c.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decoration placement</h2>Enrich it using a library of prebuilt decorations like: mushrooms, bridges, statues and so on...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d8b3076cff66389c846717840f690202.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d8b3076cff66389c846717840f690202.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d8b3076cff66389c846717840f690202.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/49adeeaa95448d96caf8dbf6fcf0bd88.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/49adeeaa95448d96caf8dbf6fcf0bd88.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/49adeeaa95448d96caf8dbf6fcf0bd88.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scene customization</h2>Customize the scene as you like.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/8524ce31678b1e0c085d5382c039edef.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/8524ce31678b1e0c085d5382c039edef.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/8524ce31678b1e0c085d5382c039edef.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Have you ever dreamed about building a terrarium? Do you already have one, but it’s not enough? Or maybe you want to test yourself before making the real one? Terrarium Builder is a game for you! In Terrarium Builder you can design and create realistic terrariums with the following features:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Terrain Sculpting</h2>Sculpt the terrain with different brushes, so that you can achieve the shape that you want.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/0874fce21c666776b3908bd26d3e4eb4.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/0874fce21c666776b3908bd26d3e4eb4.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/0874fce21c666776b3908bd26d3e4eb4.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Terrain Painting</h2>Paint typical surfaces like grass, moss, and the terrain itself.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d9490acc228ce31f4e851da84bdda45c.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d9490acc228ce31f4e851da84bdda45c.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d9490acc228ce31f4e851da84bdda45c.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decoration placement</h2>Enrich it using a library of prebuilt decorations like: mushrooms, bridges, statues and so on...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d8b3076cff66389c846717840f690202.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d8b3076cff66389c846717840f690202.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/d8b3076cff66389c846717840f690202.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/49adeeaa95448d96caf8dbf6fcf0bd88.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/49adeeaa95448d96caf8dbf6fcf0bd88.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/49adeeaa95448d96caf8dbf6fcf0bd88.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scene customization</h2>Customize the scene as you like.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/8524ce31678b1e0c085d5382c039edef.poster.avif?t=1677573247\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/8524ce31678b1e0c085d5382c039edef.webm?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208300/extras/8524ce31678b1e0c085d5382c039edef.mp4?t=1677573247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
